QuestData.Title: Growing the Farm II: Knock on Wood
QuestData.Description: Sure! I know just the wagon that you're talkin' about!$B$BI can fix it right up, but I'll need wood.$B$BThere's a whole lot of it down at the bottom of the lake. If you fish it right out - haha, get it? Fish? Oh I just crack myself up sometimes.$B$BAnyway, you bring me here some 'o that wood and then I'll get right to work!
